         <div type="commentary">
             <p>This inscription is edited twice by <bibl><ptr target="bib:Nakanishi+Hinuber2014_01"/></bibl>, as II.2,20 and II.2,21. It corresponds to <bibl><ptr target="bib:Poonacha2011_01"/><citedRange unit="item">223</citedRange></bibl>.The break on the stone under the <foreign>akṣara</foreign> <foreign>ka</foreign>, visible in both pictures published by the editors make it rather clear it is a same stone, despite the hesitation expressed by them.</p>
